flowchart TD
    A([Prediction request: entity IDs]) --> B[Validate request schema]
    B --> C{Valid?}
    C -- No --> D([Return 400 Bad Request])
    C -- Yes --> E[Fetch features from online feature store]
    E --> F{All features found?}
    F -- Missing --> G[Compute missing features in real time]
    G --> H[Assemble feature vector]
    F -- Found --> H
    H --> I[Look up active model version from registry]
    I --> J[Model forward pass]
    J --> K[Post-process: calibration and decoding]
    K --> L{Cache eligible?}
    L -- Yes --> M[Write prediction to cache with TTL]
    M --> N[Log features + model version + prediction]
    L -- No --> N
    N --> O([Return prediction response])
